---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Design System"
  description="Anteprima del tema configurato in src/styles/theme.css + env"
  noindex
>
  <main class="min-h-svh bg-background text-foreground">
    <header class="border-b border-border">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-12">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
            <h1 class="font-sans text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">Design System</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              Anteprima del tema corrente. Modifica
              <code class="font-mono">src/styles/theme.css</code> per i colori, o le
              <code class="font-mono">PUBLIC_FONT_*</code> in <code class="font-mono">.env</code>
              per la tipografia.
            </p>
          </div>
          <button
            id="theme-toggle"
            class="shrink-0 rounded-md border border-border bg-secondary px-4 py-2 font-sans text-sm text-secondary-foreground shadow-xs transition-colors hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground"
          >
            Toggle theme
          </button>
        </div>
        <nav class="mt-6 font-sans text-sm">
          <a class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground" href="/">← Home</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-24 px-6 py-16">
      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 font-sans text-3xl font-bold">Tipografia</h2>
        <p class="mb-10 font-sans text-muted-foreground">
          Tre ruoli configurabili via <code class="font-mono">.env</code>:
          <code class="font-mono">--font-sans</code>, <code class="font-mono">--font-serif</code>,
          <code class="font-mono">--font-mono</code>.
        </p>

        <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <div class="mb-4 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-muted-foreground uppercase">
              Headings · font-serif
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3 font-serif">
              <h1 class="text-5xl leading-tight font-bold">Heading 1</h1>
              <h2 class="text-4xl leading-tight font-bold">Heading 2</h2>
              <h3 class="text-3xl leading-snug font-semibold">Heading 3</h3>
              <h4 class="text-2xl leading-snug font-semibold">Heading 4</h4>
              <h5 class="text-xl font-medium">Heading 5</h5>
              <h6 class="text-lg font-medium">Heading 6</h6>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="mb-4 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-muted-foreground uppercase">
              Headings · font-sans
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3 font-sans">
              <h1 class="text-5xl leading-tight font-bold">Heading 1</h1>
              <h2 class="text-4xl leading-tight font-bold">Heading 2</h2>
              <h3 class="text-3xl leading-snug font-semibold">Heading 3</h3>
              <h4 class="text-2xl leading-snug font-semibold">Heading 4</h4>
              <h5 class="text-xl font-medium">Heading 5</h5>
              <h6 class="text-lg font-medium">Heading 6</h6>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <div class="mb-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-wide text-muted-foreground uppercase">
              Body · font-sans
            </div>
            <p class="max-w-prose font-sans leading-relaxed">
              Paragrafo in sans serif. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed
              do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
              <em>Italico</em> e <strong>grassetto</strong> per enfasi.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="mb-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-wide text-muted-foreground uppercase">
              Body · font-serif
            </div>
            <p class="max-w-prose font-serif leading-relaxed">
              Paragrafo in serif. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do
              eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
              <em>Italico</em> e <strong>grassetto</strong> per enfasi.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <div class="mb-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-wide text-muted-foreground uppercase">
            Code · font-mono
          </div>
          <pre
            class="overflow-x-auto rounded-md border border-border bg-card p-4 font-mono text-sm text-card-foreground">
const greet = (name: string): string =&gt;
  &apos;Ciao, &apos; + name + &apos;! Benvenuto nel design system.&apos;
          </pre>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs tracking-wide text-muted-foreground uppercase">
          Esempio · Hero
        </div>
        <h2 class="mb-8 font-sans text-3xl font-bold">Landing hero</h2>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-10 shadow-sm sm:p-16">
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-6 text-center">
            <span
              class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-border bg-accent px-3 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-accent-foreground"
            >
              v0.2.0 · design system
            </span>
            <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl leading-[1.1] font-bold sm:text-6xl">
              Build a marketing site, <span class="text-primary">in minutes</span>.
            </h1>
            <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg text-muted-foreground sm:text-xl">
              Un template Astro v6 forkabile, con design tokens shadcn-style, tipografia env-driven
              e tutto il quality gate già pronto. Compila <code class="font-mono text-sm">.env</code
              > e fai deploy.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 pt-2">
              <a
                href="#"
                class="rounded-md bg-primary px-6 py-2.5 font-sans font-medium text-primary-foreground shadow-sm transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
              >
                Forka il template
              </a>
              <a
                href="#"
                class="rounded-md border border-border bg-secondary px-6 py-2.5 font-sans font-medium text-secondary-foreground transition-colors hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground"
              >
                Leggi i docs
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs tracking-wide text-muted-foreground uppercase">
          Esempio · Article
        </div>
        <h2 class="mb-8 font-sans text-3xl font-bold">Long-form content</h2>

        <article class="mx-auto max-w-prose">
          <div class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs tracking-wide text-muted-foreground uppercase">
            12 marzo 2026 · 8 min lettura
          </div>
          <h1 class="mb-4 font-serif text-4xl leading-tight font-bold">
            L'arte di scegliere una palette
          </h1>
          <p class="mb-8 font-sans text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Tre principi per evitare i colori "da template" e dare al tuo sito un'identità
            riconoscibile fin dal primo sguardo.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-4 font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor
            incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud
            exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 font-serif text-2xl font-bold">Un neutral tinted vale dieci</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat
            nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui
            officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.
          </p>

          <blockquote
            class="my-8 border-l-4 border-primary pl-6 font-serif text-xl leading-relaxed text-foreground italic"
          >
            "Un grigio puro è una rinuncia. Un grigio tinted è una scelta."
          </blockquote>

          <h3 class="mt-8 mb-2 font-sans text-xl font-semibold">Una piccola checklist</h3>
          <ul class="mb-6 list-inside list-disc space-y-1 font-sans leading-relaxed">
            <li>Parti dal neutral, non dal primary.</li>
            <li>Verifica i contrasti AA su tutti i ruoli.</li>
            <li>Lascia spazio per il <code class="font-mono text-sm">--accent</code>.</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque
            laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis.
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs tracking-wide text-muted-foreground uppercase">
          Esempio · Feature grid
        </div>
        <h2 class="mb-8 font-sans text-3xl font-bold">Cosa offre il template</h2>

        <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          {
            [
              {
                label: '01',
                title: 'Quality gates inclusi',
                body: 'TypeScript strict, ESLint v10 type-aware, Prettier, Vitest, Playwright e Knip già configurati e in CI.',
              },
              {
                label: '02',
                title: 'Theming env-driven',
                body: 'Pochi token in .env per font, dark mode, view transitions. I colori in src/styles/theme.css, shadcn-style.',
              },
              {
                label: '03',
                title: 'Release automatizzate',
                body: 'release-please bumpa la versione e scrive il CHANGELOG dai Conventional Commits. Dependabot tiene tutto fresco.',
              },
            ].map(({ label, title, body }) => (
              <div class="group cursor-pointer rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-primary hover:bg-accent">
                <div class="mb-4 inline-flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-accent font-mono text-sm text-accent-foreground transition-colors group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-primary-foreground">
                  {label}
                </div>
                <h3 class="mb-2 font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-card-foreground">{title}</h3>
                <p class="font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">{body}</p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-muted-foreground uppercase">
          Esempio · Editorial display
        </div>
        <h2 class="mb-8 font-sans text-3xl font-bold">Tipografia stravagante</h2>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-8 shadow-sm sm:p-16">
          <div class="mb-10 flex items-center gap-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-7xl leading-none font-bold text-primary sm:text-8xl">01</div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
              <div class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-muted-foreground uppercase">
                Capitolo uno
              </div>
              <div class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">Lettura · 4 min</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h1
            class="mb-10 font-serif text-5xl leading-[0.95] font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl"
          >
            Tipografia <em class="font-light text-primary italic">audace</em>,<br />
            contenuti precisi.
          </h1>

          <p
            class="mb-12 font-serif text-xl leading-relaxed first-letter:float-left first-letter:mr-3 first-letter:font-serif first-letter:text-7xl first-letter:leading-[0.85] first-letter:font-bold first-letter:text-primary"
          >
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor
            incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud
            exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
          </p>

          <figure class="my-12 border-l-8 border-primary pl-6 sm:my-16">
            <blockquote
              class="font-serif text-3xl leading-[1.05] font-medium text-foreground italic sm:text-5xl"
            >
              "Less is not more. Better is more."
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption
              class="mt-6 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-muted-foreground uppercase"
            >
              — Dieter Rams (probabilmente)
            </figcaption>
          </figure>

          <div class="grid gap-8 font-sans leading-relaxed sm:grid-cols-2">
            <p>
              Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat
              nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui
              officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.
            </p>
            <p>
              Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque
              laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi
              architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 border-t border-border pt-8">
            <div>
              <div class="font-mono text-4xl font-bold text-foreground sm:text-5xl">22</div>
              <div class="mt-1 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-muted-foreground uppercase">
                palette
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-mono text-4xl font-bold text-foreground sm:text-5xl">3×3</div>
              <div class="mt-1 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-muted-foreground uppercase">
                font roles
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-mono text-4xl font-bold text-foreground sm:text-5xl">100%</div>
              <div class="mt-1 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-muted-foreground uppercase">
                test coverage
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 font-sans text-3xl font-bold">Colori</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 font-sans text-muted-foreground">
          Token semantici stile shadcn. Definiti in
          <code class="font-mono">src/styles/theme.css</code>, agganciati a utility Tailwind via
          <code class="font-mono">@theme inline</code>.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-border bg-background p-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-foreground">--background</div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">--foreground</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-border bg-card p-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-card-foreground">--card</div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">--card-foreground</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-border bg-popover p-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-popover-foreground">--popover</div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">--popover-foreground</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-primary p-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground">--primary</div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-primary-foreground/70">--primary-foreground</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-secondary p-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-secondary-foreground">--secondary</div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-secondary-foreground/70">--secondary-foreground</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-muted p-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-foreground">--muted</div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">--muted-foreground</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-accent p-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-accent-foreground">--accent</div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-accent-foreground/70">--accent-foreground</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-destructive p-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-destructive-foreground">
              --destructive
            </div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-destructive-foreground/70">
              --destructive-foreground
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2 rounded-md border border-border p-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">--border / --input / --ring</div>
            <div class="h-px bg-border"></div>
            <div class="h-px bg-input"></div>
            <div class="h-px bg-ring"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 font-sans text-3xl font-bold">Border radius</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 font-sans text-muted-foreground">
          Tutte derivate via <code class="font-mono">calc()</code> dal token base
          <code class="font-mono">--radius</code>.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-sm bg-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">rounded-sm</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">rounded-md</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">rounded-lg</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">rounded-xl</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">rounded-2xl</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-3xl bg-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">rounded-3xl</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-4xl bg-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">rounded-4xl</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 font-sans text-3xl font-bold">Shadow</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 font-sans text-muted-foreground">
          Scala fissa di shadow. Su tema dark le shadow sono volutamente sottili (sfondi scuri
          riducono il contrasto naturale).
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-card p-8 text-center shadow-2xs">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">shadow-2xs</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-card p-8 text-center shadow-xs">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">shadow-xs</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-card p-8 text-center shadow-sm">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">shadow-sm</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-card p-8 text-center shadow">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">shadow</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-card p-8 text-center shadow-md">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">shadow-md</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-card p-8 text-center shadow-lg">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">shadow-lg</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-card p-8 text-center shadow-xl">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">shadow-xl</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md bg-card p-8 text-center shadow-2xl">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-card-foreground">shadow-2xl</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<script is:inline>
  document.getElementById('theme-toggle')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const isDark = document.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark')
    localStorage.setItem('theme', isDark ? 'dark' : 'light')
  })
</script>
